task.summary: Recreates handles after releasing the mouse and after changing the viewport.
Must compare return value with new value and not old value!
Renames ReadableList/Set/Collection to ReadOnlyList/Set/Collection for consistency with JavaFX API. Adds ImmutableList/Set/Collection interfaces.
Renames ViewController to ActivityViewController because the name ViewController is too generic.
Stroke style now always writes the stroke width.
More handles take now colors and size from DrawingView.
Adds zoom +/- buttons. Increase zoomable range.
